item.title: 【HD Live Performances】Taylor Swift - The Eras Tour - 2023-07-22 - Seattle, WA (First Row Audience Recording)
item.description:
Here's an amazing first row audience recording of The Eras Tour, best one I've seen so far!

This is the raw file that I captured from YouTube, the video got taken down in less than a day. And I wanted to share this awesome recording for those who missed out!

Sadly, I don't remember the account name of uploader, it was probably "Ralph ...." or something. Anways, if someone knows it pls let me know.

Huge shout-out to the OG uploader for recording and sharing this amazing footage!

Enjoy!
